{"tid":1879681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》日本一天增4例 東奧籌委會：奧運不會取消或延期","createTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T14:30:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":54,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9243d3c21f4c304ce56a35544de0bc2b7a7cb5","tid":1879681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/13/phpc5qE30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F13%2Fphpc5qE30.jpg&h=abfd04fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京奧運籌委會與國際奧會（IOC）今起在東京舉行為期2天的會議。右為籌委會主席森喜朗，左為IOC協調委員會主席柯茲。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本今（13）日一口氣新增4例武漢肺炎（COVID-19）病例，在疫情籠罩之下，東京奧運籌委會在與國際奧會（IOC）舉行為期2天的會議開始時，重申2020年的奧運不會取消或延期。<br />\n<br />\n《美聯社》報導，距離東京奧運開幕僅剩5個月，聖火傳遞也即將在下月開跑，東奧籌委會主席森喜朗今日通過口譯對聚集在東京的數十名IOC官員說，「我們想再次說明，我們不考慮把比賽取消或延期。」<br />\n<br />\n日本今日新增4例境內感染個案，包括首例死亡個案，該疫情發展將讓籌委會和IOC的官員更加不安。截至目前，日本國內確診總數已達33例，另外鑽石公主號郵輪有218人確診。<br />\n<br />\n這次到東京出席會議的IOC官員中，包括醫學及科學主任巴吉特博士（Dr. Richard Budgett），他並不常出差進行這類視察。<br />\n<br />\n受到疫情影響，一級方程式賽車原定4月在上海登場的中國大獎賽12日宣布延期；國際七人制橄欖球賽的香港站和新加坡站，確定從4月延期到10月，世界橄欖球總會（World Rugby）今日表示，與奧運有關的活動將不會如期在4月於北京舉行。<br />\n<br />\nIOC協調委員會主席柯茲（John Coates）負責定期檢查東京奧運籌備進度。他說，希望從日本政府、東京都政府和籌委會收到有關該疫情的報告，以便了解「正在採取的必要預防措施」。"},{"pid":"2227a2d233c0c826023a524e87681d5a8c285d94","tid":1879681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3067507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3067507&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=082ee719\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3067507&h=278dc0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3067507</a>"},{"pid":"2182af022b533f8d13cfb83403b436c1f41eaede","tid":1879681,"uid":45518,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"gogogo"},{"pid":"af4a14ddbbe10c697eaafe39fa53706343b800d1","tid":1879681,"uid":321345,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"仲有運動員敢嚟咩"},{"pid":"e01747a7100e99e563ba9af634cb14852d948b91","tid":1879681,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"OK GL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c683bce842cb8890d109b6927e1650fb66c98dca","tid":1879681,"uid":138964,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之,美國開口講到今年唔會疫情完結<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ebe9764bff1b12f2f174eb93d77e160d39f909","tid":1879681,"uid":49853,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"只可以話日本唔好彩、俾中國累撚死"},{"pid":"81ed7dc4145ee7af59620c9596b6d457972aadb2","tid":1879681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4a14ddbbe10c697eaafe39fa53706343b800d1","tid":1879681,"uid":321345,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"仲有運動員敢嚟咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"有！"},{"pid":"5e2d7c0719deaa43416310b64f2f6d7318ed6821","tid":1879681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91fc3be2db1b3fad1fa27140abc979eee5e9157","tid":1879681,"uid":150983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"東京奧運之謎"},{"pid":"125f02897ea9f0d9866ee8f4165d990e4e803fbd","tid":1879681,"uid":314531